00:14:32.200 --> 00:14:35.069
So, that's why I sound annoyed. Um

00:14:35.079 --> 00:14:37.470
if I sound condescending, I guarantee

00:14:37.480 --> 00:14:39.270
you I'm really not with this stuff. It's

00:14:39.280 --> 00:14:41.510
actually very easy to learn this. We've

00:14:41.520 --> 00:14:43.630
