the reason that you can't play against

00:39:21.720 --> 00:39:24.190
the model to train it is that the amount

00:39:24.200 --> 00:39:26.430
of gameplay data that you would give it

00:39:26.440 --> 00:39:27.830
by doing that is essentially

00:39:27.840 --> 00:39:29.470
meaningless.

