00:39:32.760 --> 00:39:34.750
hundreds of millions of steps worth of

00:39:34.760 --> 00:39:37.270
data often, like hours, days, weeks,

00:39:37.280 --> 00:39:40.150
sometimes years or decades or more of

00:39:40.160 --> 00:39:42.550
simulated data. It happens very quickly

00:39:42.560 --> 00:39:44.430
cuz the simulations are run way faster

00:39:44.440 --> 00:39:47.190
than real time.

00:39:47.200 --> 00:39:48.470
But the amount of data that you would

00:39:48.480 --> 00:39:51.670
give them is just very, very low.

00:39:51.680 --> 00:39:53.390
And um we can just train them in

00:39:53.400 --> 00:41:26.990
simulation on their own.

